%description
Performs hypothesis testing using the interval estimates (e.g., confidence
intervals). The non-overlapping interval estimates indicates the
statistical significance. References to these procedures can be found at
Noguchi and Marmolejo-Ramos (2016) <doi:10.1080/00031305.2016.1200487>,
Bonett and Seier (2003) <doi:10.1198/0003130032323>, and Lemm (2006)
<doi:10.1300/J082v51n02_05>.

